   the symmetries that enforce such spin texture in a chiral crystal, thus
   bringing new insight in the formation of a spin vectorial field more
   complex than the previously proposed hedgehog configuration. Our
   findings thus pave the way to a classification scheme for these exotic
   spin textures and their search in chiral crystals.},
